 Joe Hurtuk of Bedford won the 2011 Ohio Mid-Amateur Golf Championship in a playoff today, following up his first round score of 2-under par 70 with a solid 71 then making par on the first extra hole for victory.   [Read more ?]  

					 

					   

			

					
			

