					  2010 Ohio Am Entry Form Now Available  

					 by Allen Freeman  |  March 2, 2010    No Comments  

					 

 Entry blanks for the 2010 Ohio Amateur Golf Championship at Kirtland Country Club are now available! See the  OGA’s tournament schedule page  for details and to download a PDF entry blank, or you can apply online (extra fee). 
 Qualifying tournaments in the Northeast Ohio area will be played on May 24th at both Elyria Country Club and Youngstown Country Club, and there are other qualifier dates and locations throughout the state as shown on the schedule. The entry fee for a member of an OGA club is $150, for a non-member player the entry fee is $175. 
 The Ohio Amateur will be played July 13-16. Get your entry form submitted soon to ensure a spot! 

					 

					   

			

					
			

