					  Ohio Amateur Entry Due Friday  

					 by Allen Freeman  |  May 10, 2009    No Comments  

					 

 If you are interested in qualifying for the 2009 Ohio Amateur Championship (or are already exempt), you must submit an entry blank to the OGA by this Friday, May 15 at 4 p.m. The local qualifier will be conducted at Fox Meadows CC on Tuesday, May 26, and the tournament proper is at Moraine CC in Dayton July 13-17. Players can  enter online  or  print and mail an entry blank . 

					 

					   

			

					
			

