					  2008 Ohio Am Cleveland Qualifier Results  

					 by Allen Freeman  |  May 27, 2008    No Comments  

					 

 The local qualifier for the 2008 Ohio Amateur Championship was held Tuesday, May 27 at Elyria Country Club. Dan Rush of Avon grabbed medalist honors with a smooth 3-under par 69, winning by two shots over Ben Cavey of Wadsworth and Zach Glassman of Highland Heights. 
 A score of 76 was needed to advance to the tournament proper, to be held at Findlay Country Club July 15-18. 
 Complete results for all players who participated in the qualifier are  posted here . 
 –Allen Freeman 

					 

					   

			

					
			

				 

			

				
 
